Welcome to Orenda at Othello Square
This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 607 Sq.
Live in one of the most diverse zip codes in the nation with authentic neighborhood cafes and shopping.
Just steps from the Othello Light Rail Station you are minutes from Columbia City, Downtown, Capitol Hill, University of Washington, SeaTac Airport, and all that Seattle offers.
Enjoy the neighborhood parks and playgrounds or take one of our RAD Power Bikes to the shores of Lake Washington.
And don’t let the Seattle drizzle keep in you indoors, our rooftop deck features a canopy and heaters to enjoy the views of Mt. Rainier all year long.

Stainless steel appliance package, Full-sized in-unit washer and dryer, Eco-conscious materials, Lofty ceilings for abundant natural light, Choice of fire and ice kitchen colors, Select units have exterior deck or balcony, Quartz countertops

Rooftop pet terrace, Secure package lockers, Underground parking, Indoor lounge that opens to outdoor rooftop entertaining, Fitness center with boxing, cardio, and strength training, Rooftop gas firepits and comfy seating, Bike room with repair station and rinse area, Rooftop deck with southern views of Mt. Rainier, Indoor shuffleboard, pool table, arcade games, Steps from Othello Light Rail Station, Rooftop canopy area with heaters for year-round use, Rooftop EVO, BBQ grill and sink, Indoor communal kitchen and media center
